        </li>
              <li data-thumb="https://cdn.arstechnica.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/demo4-150x150.jpg" data-src="https://cdn.arstechnica.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/demo4.jpg" data-responsive="https://cdn.arstechnica.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/demo4-980x649.jpg 1080, https://cdn.arstechnica.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/demo4.jpg 2560" data-sub-html="#caption-1974286">
          <figure style="height:668px;">
            <div class="image" style="background-image:url('https://cdn.arstechnica.net/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/demo4-980x649.jpg'); background-color:#000"></div>
